{"name":"Animal Spirit Guides","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/nature/wolf-paw-glow-purple-teal.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 20\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>At 1st level, a shaman gains a random animal spirit guide in exchange for a permanent loss of 1 point from a random attribute score.</p>\n<p>The spirit guide imparts the wisdom necessary to cast spells, and &ldquo;marks&rdquo; the shaman with a permanent special ability that reflects their bond. (q.v., Appendix G for possible spirit animals and their abilities).</p>\n<p>Neutral shamans have a single guide throughout their career, but the efficacy of their special ability incre- ments at levels 4, 8, and 12.</p>\n<p>Chaotic shamans may acquire an additional spirit guide at levels 4, 8, and 12. Each new guide reduces a random ability by 1 point, but if the same guide is rolled, the corresponding special ability increments.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"shaman-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_zlg7vwx3m5","path":"Shaman","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"058hAbZaTCwI6N25"}
{"name":"After Reaching 9th Level","type":"ability","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-open-red.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 41\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>When the beast-talker reaches 9th level, all animals in the home range treat the beast-talker as an equal: Chaotic beasts restrain hostility (+4 to reactions) while Neutral and Law- ful beasts are kind and helpful. Beasts of any alignment will also warn the beast-talker of intruders and danger to the range, pass messages, and aid in the local defence.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"beast-talker-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_4jlmlo6pda2","path":"Beast-talker","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.bX8ZYinwnzbKi52Y"}},"_id":"0BGpXGHBUm6zJZoS"}
