{"name":"Bardic Songs","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/sonic/projectile-shock-wave-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 65\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>&bull; 1st Level: <strong>Charm Person, Protection from Evil, Shield, Sleep </strong></p>\n<p>&bull; 2nd Level: <strong>Continual Light, ESP , Locate Object, Phantasmal Force </strong></p>\n<p>&bull; 3rd Level: <strong>Clairvoyance, Dispel Magic, Hold Person, Protection from Evil 10&rsquo; Radius, Protection from Normal Missiles </strong></p>\n<p>&bull; 4th Level: <strong>Charm Monster, Con- fusion, Hallucinatory Terrain, Wizard Eye</strong></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"bard-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_ampjsspqo9d","path":"Bard","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"1IO9kPfTKDGMbOQj"}
{"name":"Home Range","type":"ability","img":"icons/environment/wilderness/terrain-forest-gray.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 41\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Any time after reaching 2nd level, the beast-talker may establish a home range by clearing a wilderness hex of hostile monsters and humanoids. Each level thereaf- ter, they may extend the range by another (adjacent) hex, provided they can &ldquo;tame&rdquo; the territory. The range must be continuous but may include wilderness terrain of any type. Within their home range, beast-talkers gain a +1 bonus to surprise, animal reactions, initiative, &ldquo;to-hit,&rdquo; and damage rolls.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"beast-talker-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_4jlmlo6pda2","path":"Beast-talker","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"1rlPi6W97QXeEJ1E"}
