{"name":"Animal Totems","type":"ability","img":"icons/creatures/mammals/elk-moose-marked-green.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 21\">\n<div title=\"Page 43\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Each animal totem grants defensive bonuses against certain attack types. Below are three examples inspired by the Norse epics:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Bear: +2 save vs. fire, &ndash;2 dam- age from edged weapons. Typical arms: axe, sword; furs, shield.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Boar: +1 save vs. death, &ndash;2 damage from blunt weapons. Typical arms: dagger, spear, sword; leather.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Wolf: +2 save vs. fire, &ndash;2 damage from missiles. Typical arms: spear; furs.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"berserker-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"Item.ttcFitngPi8V7g6H"},"cf":{"id":"temp_00v93s2o1qg","path":"Berserker","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"3BZ3CyJQ5Ka7Xs6H"}
