{"name":"After Reaching 10th Level","type":"ability","img":"icons/sundries/books/book-open-red.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 27\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>At 10th level, an elder may build a temple-stronghold dedicated to their deity, attracting 20-80 (2d4x10) 1st level dwarfs and 5-10 (1d6+4) 1st level elders. The settlement where the stronghold is built cannot al- ready have a temple to the charac- ter&rsquo;s deity. Once the stronghold is established, the elder becomes a local clan head and is expected to tend to the deity&rsquo;s worshippers, aid in the local defence, and apply the deity&rsquo;s powers (i.e., divine spells) to the common good. At each experi- ence level after 10th, the elder at- tracts an additional 10-40 dwarfs and 1d4 elders.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"elder-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_zyg4myb00sl","path":"Elder, Dwarf","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.4D8j97xORQ4vxoq1"}},"_id":"AVyyI0Obpi2anJyf"}
