{"name":"Combat","type":"ability","img":"icons/skills/melee/swords-parry-block-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<p>Crusaders can use any weapons permitted by their order, and they are able to wear any armor including shields.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>When fighting the infidel, crusaders gain +1 to initiative, &ldquo;to- hit,&rdquo; and damage rolls; a +1 bonus to their AC and saving throws vs. infidel attacks; and all allies within 20&rsquo; enjoy the effects of bless.</p>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"crusader-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_sgyztgev1h8","path":"Crusader","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"JXsSHOwgpp11Y0Ql"}
