{"name":"Drain Vitality","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/unholy/strike-hand-glow-pink.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 54\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Once per level each day, a necromancer may drain a target&rsquo;s vitality at a range of 5&rsquo; per level. This power is equivalent to the 1st level cleric spell <strong>cause light wounds</strong>, though the hit points drained are transferred to the necromancer. Hit points thus gained may exceed the necromancer&rsquo;s maximum, but these &ldquo;extra&rdquo; hit points dissipate after 1 turn per level.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"necromancer-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tgb4y2pvwv","path":"Necromancer","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"P1qISIlpVd8WUCz6"}
