{"name":"Scouting Missions","type":"ability","img":"icons/sundries/documents/blueprint-magical-brown.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 67\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div title=\"Page 67\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>While scouts prefer to operate in- dependently, local authorities may call on them to:</p>\n<p>&bull; Escort travellers<br />&bull; Guide explorers or soldiers<br />&bull; Conduct reconnaissance<br />&bull; Find/rescue lost individuals<br />&bull; Parley with wilderness denizens</p>\n<p>&bull; Eliminate threats in the wild</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"scout-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_yykl5k5ajoq","path":"Scout","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"cox3el4IX4XcugtH"}
