{"name":"Shape Change","type":"ability","img":"icons/creatures/mammals/wolf-howl-moon-forest-blue.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 20\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>At 4th level, a shaman may assume the form of any of their animal guides; this ability conforms in all respects to the 4th level magic-user spell <strong>polymorph self</strong> and may be used once per day for every four levels the shaman has earned.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"shaman-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_zlg7vwx3m5","path":"Shaman","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.0SyCaryRf8TO0Hap"}},"_id":"rJ4PaDH6KbzreFgQ"}
{"name":"Divine Magic","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue%20.webp","data":{"description":"<p>See @Compendium[old-school-essentials.ose journals.rDANNhKgVb1HJk0V]{Magic}for full details on divine magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Deity disfavour</strong>:&nbsp;Crusaders are bound by the same standards as their clerical counterparts; if their alignment strays from that of their deity, they cannot cast spells until reconciled.</p>\n<p><strong>Magical research</strong>:&nbsp;Dedicated to martial pursuits, crusaders do not engage in magical research.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell casting</strong>:&nbsp;Crusaders may pray for divine spells, following the same rules for divine spell use as clerics.</p>\n<p><strong>Using magic items</strong>: Crusaders may use magic items reserved for clerics, including divine spell scrolls.</p>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"crusader-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_sgyztgev1h8","path":"Crusader","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.Rzc3WPU7y9KAd1Ua"}},"_id":"rJQMMlFDqGiN9K0w"}
