{"name":"Arcane Magic","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue%20.webp","data":{"description":"<p>See @Compendium[old-school-essentials.ose journals.rDANNhKgVb1HJk0V]{Magic} for full details on arcane magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Magical research</strong>:&nbsp;Necromancers may conduct magical research as magic-users; they must reach 9th level before creating magic items (ex- cept for creating golems, as above).</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Spell casting</strong>:&nbsp;Necromancers cast spells as a magic-user of equal level. N.B. Corpses revived with the 5th level magic-user spell <strong>animate dead</strong> have maximum hit points.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong>Using magic items</strong>: Necromancers may use magic items reserved for magic-users, including scrolls.</p>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"necromancer-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_tgb4y2pvwv","path":"Necromancer","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.GEThpLA7ZMrcVsV5"}},"_id":"sIyhEFClqUjDe3Zd"}
