{"name":"Arcane Magic","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-blue%20.webp","data":{"description":"<p>See @Compendium[old-school-essentials.ose journals.rDANNhKgVb1HJk0V]{Magic} for full details on arcane magic.</p>\n<p><strong>Magical research</strong>: A sorcerer of any level may spend time and money on magical research. This allows them to add new spells to their spell book and to research other magical effects. When a sorcerer reaches 9th level, they are also able to create magic items.</p>\n<p><strong>Spell casting</strong>:&nbsp;Sorcerers may cast 1 spell level per level each day (e.g., a 3rd level sorcerer could cast three 1st level spells, one 3rd level spell, or one 1st and one 2nd level spell). If the spell&rsquo;s level exceeds the sorcerer&rsquo;s Max. Spell Level, or if they wish to cast additional spells, they must petition their patron with a reaction roll. The sorcerer gains a +1 bonus to reaction rolls by sacrificing 1hp per spell level (e.g., a 5th level spell re- quires the sacrifice of 5hp for a +1 bonus, 10hp for +2, etc.). Sacrificed hit points heal at the normal rate.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div title=\"Page 56\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Spell Acquisition</strong>: A sorcerer has full access to the entire arcane spell list but must acquire each spell by peti- tioning an extra-planar patron via a reaction roll (q.v., &ldquo;Patron Reactions&rdquo; on facing page). Finding a patron costs 1,000gp and 1 week per spell level of research and sacrifice; if the spell is refused, the sorcerer may seek a different patron. Once a spell is acquired, that patron is the sorcerer&rsquo;s <em>only</em> source of the spell&mdash; no other patron will bestow it.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p><strong>Using magic items</strong>: As spell casters, sorcerers are able to use magic scrolls of spells on their spell list. They can also use items that may only be used by arcane spell casters (e.g. magic wands).</p>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"sorcerer-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_fxq21opdmjb","path":"Sorcerer","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.GEThpLA7ZMrcVsV5"}},"_id":"FaweyrVzc8joDrCc"}
