{"name":"Patron Reactions","type":"ability","img":"icons/magic/symbols/runes-star-pentagon-magenta.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 57\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>When petitioning a patron for a new spell, a spell above the sorcerer&rsquo;s Max Spell Level, or additional spell levels in a day, the sorcerer makes a reaction roll: Subtract the spell&rsquo;s level and apply a &ndash;1 penalty if alignments differ; add the Max # of Patrons figure, CHA adjustment, and any hit point sacrifice.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"sorcerer-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_fxq21opdmjb","path":"Sorcerer","color":"#000000"}},"_id":"6jRI98s9ZcO0MHan"}
{"name":"Restrictions","type":"ability","img":"icons/skills/social/trading-justice-scale-yellow.webp","data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 40\">\n<div title=\"Page 48\">\n<div title=\"Page 56\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><strong>Alignment</strong>: Sorcerers may be of any alignment, but they cannot seek patrons of the opposite alignment.</p>\n<p><strong>Pledge</strong>: Should a sorcerer act contrary to a patron&rsquo;s agenda, they cannot petition that patron for spells until loyalty is reaffirmed.</p>\n<p><strong>Talisman</strong>: In lieu of spell books, sorcerers must bear a talisman (ring, brooch, pin, etc.) for each patron they serve, signifying their right to engage in arcane pacts; spells can- not be loosed without it.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>","autoTags":[],"manualTags":[],"save":"","pattern":"white","requirements":"sorcerer-bxo","roll":"","rollType":"result","rollTarget":0,"blindroll":false},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"PxqQojdX3Ghz8Uq5":3},"flags":{"cf":{"id":"temp_fxq21opdmjb","path":"Sorcerer","color":"#000000"},"core":{"sourceId":"Compendium.old-school-essentials.ose abilities.GqQd4Cp1UrsQQneu"}},"_id":"czLLMJdrGyi3G41F"}
